\n<br />\n通常真正分開嘅原因都係好個人既野， 唔計錢嗰啲啦，<br />\n<br />\n而個性幾乎唔會太大改變， 以前會覺得一啲明明有感情都果斷分手嘅人點解咁絕情， 而家會覺得其實佢哋 睇透咗呢樣野， <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個人就算變得優秀，<br />\n佢嘅內核都好難會變咗另一個人，<br />\n最後會嘈嘅位都係會嘈"},{"pid":"a5cd8a63acff9e550e63d5d61350b706ece23204","tid":2425902,"uid":228213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"902be751af5a0068ab6b7b829bcecce74720d290","tid":2425902,"uid":282490,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T15:58:09.000Z","msg":"主動講分手果個只係咁啱理智佔上風 <br />\n<br />\n做左開口果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本大家都知拖拖拉拉落去都無意思<br />\n雙方都覺得對方變左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總有人要先離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"係呀，只不過主動開口嗰個 唔使面對嗰份唔甘心"},{"pid":"4c7da3d317dc59d823818391dd85a2b70c7cbc17","tid":2425902,"uid":340364,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"當初自己都有試過挽回<br />\n鼓起勇氣打通咗電話<br />\n佢一聽到我把聲即刻cut鳩我線<br />\nOk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> is fine<br />\n他日 你係深夜打嚟 我一定cut返你線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8410b7059d056425c432a8a29b7974774a39cc","tid":2425902,"uid":228213,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4c7da3d317dc59d823818391dd85a2b70c7cbc17","tid":2425902,"uid":340364,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"當初自己都有試過挽回<br />\n鼓起勇氣打通咗電話<br />\n佢一聽到我把聲即刻cut鳩我線<br />\nOk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> is fine<br />\n他日 你係深夜打嚟 我一定cut返你線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"有時真係要靠道氣去面對。<br />\n如果無咗道氣就會想擺低面子去求人"},{"pid":"f6030410c56d0d1ce5cb8fee68a249c36910f0f1","tid":2425902,"uid":228213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24b329c8681a257c8d4edac54313ff372542f199","tid":2425902,"uid":19989,"li